Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你已找到那兩人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,媽媽\N想不到就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說兩人在學校\N功課都是一流的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了,快去找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想\N現在正要去接他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我們明天中午就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅,你做了什麼壞事\N被點名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你不是去招惹\N校長的女兒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說,是你讓她傷透心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是來找我商量事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!說的好聽\N其實早就出軌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到嘴邊的肉\N哪有不吃的道理?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既來之…則安之吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關這件事,就等研究\N充實之後再做打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人,我來介紹一下\N就是這兩位學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道葛蘿莉亞家族吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰不知道那是\N世上鼎鼎大名的家族呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是名門世家哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘿莉亞家族想聘請本校的\N兩位高材生去當家庭教師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受這種美人的青睞\N是不可能拒絕的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了妹妹們而來的\N與我的容貌無關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天,我媽才會回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有興趣的話\N就請明天過來面試吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫做愛達娜葛蘿莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來有點嚴肅耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好女人,就是那種\N經常會讓我興奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不送到嘴邊的肉\N偏要去吃的人,拜拜!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定接受邀請\N當你的家教了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是強制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡強制的男人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄什麼家教回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!嘔!來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是姊姊的家庭老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那我的老師呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說明天才會來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!這麼豪華的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫的這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼嚴肅嘛,愛達娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得允許過你叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該叫我老師嘛?啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩子看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,昨天才突然來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不快來?\N我昨晚興奮的睡不著呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人們也還沒回來\N你乖乖的在房裡等吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等老師一到我會來告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然如果他們\N能平安的回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了,我想到一個好點子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!我好聰明哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是綺羅老師嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!我猜對了,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雪希兒\N請叫我雪希兒就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,好像遲到了,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈!哈!走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然搭富豪汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種車比較堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師,由我來開車可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有所覺悟了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,很堅固的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於知道你遲到的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很注重交通安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?咦!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車跟得好近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把速度放慢一點,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是加速嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒,方向盤,方向盤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師,我是不期待\N有這種事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種地方真的不適合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師,怎麼辦\N那輛車一直在撞我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒!加強腳力\N把裙子掀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒,你是不是會錯意了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋吉明老師已經抵達了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅到了嗎?咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,剛剛抵達\N任務好像失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我們繼續保持聯絡,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了兩個\N來路不明的男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的計畫就更難實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲早要把葛蘿莉亞家族\N一一剷除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好富豪汽車救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說路上遇到麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我做的好事,你快請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是太累了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事你考慮的如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家教那件事,你會接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先見見你女兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長女已有了一位老師了\N其他四位就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也可以把我算在內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈,開玩笑的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧!雪希兒\N帶老師去介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子很沒有禮貌哦,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼企圖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在偷聽什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從我來到這裡後\N已發現你有不尋常的動作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想說的話\N就不用說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自然會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老師是日本人\N所以我的心情很好阿!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧!讓我乾一杯以示歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美小姐是從琦玉來的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琦玉?哦,是琦玉縣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,怎麼那麼說呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來,直美小姐是養女?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個屋子裡的女兒\N每一個都是養女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不快點喝掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我就喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!酒量好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美小姐,喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你那麼多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來雪希兒也很喜歡這麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看,這麼敏感的人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人看就有快感\N內褲已經濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…聽到你這種呻吟聲\N連我都受不了了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!\N我馬上就會讓你舒舒服服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,不要直美小姐\N我會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒明明不喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人不喜歡的,哼!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是\N這麼淫蕩的女人嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如我們兩個來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美小姐老是那個樣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是這間屋裡的女兒吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,我是次女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼你穿服務生的衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我被處罰的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處罰?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!這你不用管了\N我喜歡穿這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,愛達娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到另一位老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是讀書的時間\N他到底跑到哪裡去了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他想放棄家庭教師\N這份工作了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的,他絕不是會丟下\N你這種美人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧,你到底有什麼秘密?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,好,我說,拜託你別弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小子,你到底在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,綺羅,換你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差勁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒,把她扶起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師真是溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!老師也許來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下再帶你們到處去看看\N認識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為蓋魯克老師的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是綺羅老師\N你不是對他很好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒,你不用做這些事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我是被派來侍候你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是這裡的千金小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你讓我做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人叫我來請你去吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗,我到處找你呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我去摘花,摘到睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個送你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!花都枯了\N剛剛還很漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係\N給它澆上水又會活起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,準備吃飯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做阿!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要找機會報答你的\N我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露,吃飯了,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太累了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師請你到餐廳去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不能來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,只是會有點危險而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那需不需要家庭老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭老師?更不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:21:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之,先吃飽飯再說吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很忙,不要吵我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好乖,好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈,原來雪希兒怕這傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕的,它長的很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?夏露還是不願出來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我才剛從南非回來呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果強迫她的話會有危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈,我可能醉了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒,把菜送上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師,你看我的女兒們如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,因為人很多\N不知道從誰先教才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,綺羅,這樣不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點決定就太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的料理不合我胃口\N先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!我呢?該由我開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,那就從明天開始上課吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!明天?好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來夏露的房間在這
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?進不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子有點好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來跟網路聯絡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,還是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是葛蘿莉亞的財產明細
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一個小孩子\N會對這個有興趣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露的存在對葛蘿莉亞\N家族來說似乎很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又是個學生,仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會挑選我們兩個學生來當家教\N也很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.48,0:24:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰?雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?三更半夜的\N發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,如果綺羅老師不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.12,0:24:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你晚上的伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也要你有意思的話才…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.11,0:25:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師你不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.78,0:25:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.49,0:26:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.56,0:26:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你連這種事都願意做?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.26,0:26:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡你阿!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.13,0:26:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從什麼時候開始的?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.94,0:26:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我看到你的第一眼起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.91,0:26:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深一點,再深一點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.75,0:26:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.65,0:26:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.63,0:26:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深一點,再深一點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.47,0:26:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:26:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.92,0:27:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你一定要出來\N從這裡出來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒,唔…唔…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.97,0:27:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出來了
